sentence: list all round trip flights between indianapolis and orlando , on the twenty seventh of december
sq2:
SELECT DISTINCT  '"'||v1.airport_code||'"', '"'||v2.city_code||'"',
 '"'||v2.city_name||'"', '"'||v3.airport_code||'"', '"'||v4.city_code||'"',
 '"'||v4.city_name||'"', '"'||v5.days_code||'"',
 '"'||v6.day_name||'"', v6.year, v6.month_number, v6.day_number,
 '"'||v7.flight_id||'"', '"'||v8.fare_id||'"',
 v8.round_trip_cost, '"'||v9.fare_basis_code||'"', '"'||v10.days_code||'"',
 '"'||v11.day_name||'"', v11.year, v11.month_number,
 v11.day_number FROM flight v0, airport_service v1, city v2,
 airport_service v3, city v4, days v5, date_day v6, flight_fare v7,
 fare v8, fare_basis v9, days v10, date_day v11 
WHERE (((v0.from_airport = ANY v1.airport_code) AND ((v1.city_code = ANY v2.city_code) 
AND (v2.city_name = 'INDIANAPOLIS'))) 
AND (((v0.to_airport = ANY v3.airport_code) AND ((v3.city_code = ANY v4.city_code) 
AND (v4.city_name = 'ORLANDO'))) 
AND (((v0.flight_days = ANY v5.days_code) AND ((v5.day_name = ANY v6.day_name) 
AND (((v6.year =  1993) AND (v6.month_number =  12)) 
AND (v6.day_number =  27)))) AND ((v0.flight_id = ANY v7.flight_id) 
AND ((v7.fare_id = ANY v8.fare_id) AND ((v8.round_trip_cost IS NOT NULL) 
AND ((v8.fare_basis_code = ANY v9.fare_basis_code) 
AND ((v9.basis_days = ANY v10.days_code) 
AND ((v10.day_name = ANY v11.day_name) AND (((v11.year =  1993) 
AND (v11.month_number =  12)) AND (v11.day_number =  27)))))))))));
